###Read All Users
GET http://localhost:3006/admin-api/users

###For User Deactivation
PATCH http://localhost:3006/admin-api/users/deactivate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId":"69f97318d17f3f50ff7e5717",
    "isUserActive":false
}

###For User Activation
PATCH http://localhost:3006/admin-api/users/activate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId":"69f97318d17f3f50ff7e5717",
    "isUserActive":true
}